One year ago #COVID19 arrived in NM. Now, I am 1 in 4 New Mexicans that have received their 1st #vaccine. 

NM is demonstrating how a "poor" state that prioritizes people can rise to the occasion and lead the vaccination effort. 

I'm incredibly humbled & honored 🙏🏾 https://t.co/nL9QXLhUYm https://t.co/S55zUBiznw
